WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:23.270 --> 00:00:26.000
Boil water

00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:29.000
Boil the eggs just out of the refrigerator.

00:00:29.100 --> 00:00:31.100
In a plastic bag, add 40g sugar

00:00:31.150 --> 00:00:33.100
150ml soy sauce

00:00:33.180 --> 00:00:35.100
150ml sweet sake

00:00:35.180 --> 00:00:38.300
400ml water

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:40.200
Boil for six and a half minutes.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:44.100
Place eggs in cold water

00:00:44.150 --> 00:00:46.050
Boil quail eggs for two and a half minutes.

00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:48.000
Place in water

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:53.000
Peel off the shell slowly.

00:00:53.100 --> 00:00:55.030
Soft-boiled egg yolk.

00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:57.230
It's very soft!

00:00:57.230 --> 00:01:00.290
Put the eggs in the plastic bag.

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:03.190
Put all of them in.

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:06.100
Close by twisting the opening portion.

00:01:06.100 --> 00:01:08.140
Leave in the refrigerator for a half or full day

00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:11.190
Wash your rice

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:13.250
Add 30ml Sweet sake

00:01:14.010 --> 00:01:16.160
50ml Soy sauce

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:19.030
15ml Sake

00:01:19.070 --> 00:01:21.220
Water

00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:25.080
Cook your rice.

00:01:26.150 --> 00:01:30.100
The rice is ready!

00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:34.040
Mix mix mix!

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:38.040
Your eggs should be nice and flavorful now!

00:01:38.100 --> 00:01:43.250
Cut in half and they should look like this.

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:48.100
Scoops some rice into a bowl

00:01:48.100 --> 00:01:51.200
Wrap your egg in the rice

00:01:51.250 --> 00:01:56.000
and make a rice ball.

00:02:03.100 --> 00:02:05.120
Apply your nori (seaweed) and it's done!

00:02:03.160 --> 00:02:04.160
Wrap tightly.

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:42.000
What's that?

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:49.000
I saw it!

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.000
What did you see?

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:53.000
Onigiri (Rice ball).

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:00.000
I saw it! I saw it!

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:04.000
What is it?

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.000
I don't know...

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.000
Hanjuku nitamago omusubi (Soft-boiled egg in rice balls).

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:16.000
Why only two?

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:29.000
I thought you'd say that, so I made some small ones too!

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:36.000
I'll give this to Oto.

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:43.000
Thank you. I'll little give this to Yuuma.

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:47.000
So, please put your hands together...

00:03:47.500 --> 00:03:49.000
Itadakimasu!

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:01.000
How do you like it?

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:05.000
Yummy!

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:09.000
Is there anything to drink?

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:13.000
Yuuma do you want something too?

00:04:13.500 --> 00:04:14.000
Yes!

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:18.000
Was Rino born from omusubi?

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:23.000
Of course not.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:35.000
Yuuma can eat eggs.

00:04:35.500 --> 00:04:36.000
How about Rino?

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:57.000
How did it turn out? Is it salty?

00:04:57.000 --> 00:05:00.000
Salty? Sweet?

00:05:00.500 --> 00:05:01.500
Sweet!

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:10.000
I'm going to eat another one!

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:22.000
Dirty!!

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:44.000
I won't drink anything!

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:52.000
What is this?

00:05:52.100 --> 00:05:53.000
What do you think it is?

00:05:53.100 --> 00:05:53.900
Tea.

00:05:54.100 --> 00:05:55.000
No.

00:05:55.100 --> 00:05:57.000
Grape.

00:05:57.100 --> 00:05:57.900
No.

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:06.000
Acerola.

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:08.000
Please give me a hint.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.000
I'll eat this.

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:30.000
I made five. Rino ate one.

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:35.000
There are two left. How many did Yuuma eat?

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:38.000
Two!

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:46.000
There are ten. Oto ate 15. How many are left?

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.000
Two!

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.000
Close!

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:34.000
Ten!

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:34.000
A lot of grain of rice adhering to Yuuma.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:35.866
Yuuma - there's a ton of rice stuck to you!

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:37.300
Gochisousama deshita!

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:42.000
Deshita!

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:46.000
Let's play!

